@node Main "X_marks - Documentation"

                             'X_marks' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" X_marks " link play} is a Workbench game where a number from 12 to 32 crosses
(or 'X' shapes) have been randomly hidden on an 8 by 8 tiles game
board. Your job is to find all those crosses in the fewest tries as
possible. To help you, there are various numbers at the right of
each row and bottom of each column. These numbers indicate how many
crosses are located in their respective row or column...

  Have fun!

